{"id": 1793, "genre": 1001, "title": "如今你的职场日常焦虑来自哪里？", "description": "焦虑可能是职场最普遍的一种现代病了...（题图“Giphy)", "record_count": 6310, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170718181957Bas6Gx7dcYTt5CnW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-14T03:00:57Z", "options": [{"id": 221952, "content": "朋友们加我微信du695956811", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078705}, {"id": 222208, "content": "1、上升通道；2、以才能、努力与道德为导向的公平规则和公平机会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938308}, {"id": 221953, "content": "最怕这辈子，就这样过下去了。也不知道下一步。改怎么走", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078712}, {"id": 221954, "content": "选择太多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038087}, {"id": 222210, "content": "挣不到钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533967}, {"id": 222466, "content": "待遇福利差，还要求无偿敬业奉献", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917016}, {"id": 221955, "content": "不知如何快速提升能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047397}, {"id": 222211, "content": "工作越来越多越来越难", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079902}, {"id": 221956, "content": "能力和野心的调整", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074091}, {"id": 221957, "content": "心中有追求 奈何环境不好 只能曲线救国 望有ri达成心中所愿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933016}, {"id": 222213, "content": "永远局限于每天重复的工作，毫无新鲜感可言！", "image": "img/option/option/20170716113158JueX9iLvCbHWEPnr.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079910}, {"id": 221959, "content": "该不该换家公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812943}, {"id": 222472, "content": "不会社交，感觉自己是哑巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081185}, {"id": 222728, "content": "工作能力和人际关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031607}, {"id": 221961, "content": "找不到自己的定位，无法调节情绪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068296}, {"id": 222217, "content": "希望像非洲大草原的动物们一样生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080003}, {"id": 228106, "content": "感觉混一天是一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099370}, {"id": 221963, "content": "老化太快", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054758}, {"id": 222219, "content": "世界变得太快，但是上次没有赚够。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080054}, {"id": 271884, "content": "当然是钱不够花啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950509}, {"id": 221964, "content": "很怕收邮件？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078733}, {"id": 222220, "content": "我有点晕，我想下车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080054}, {"id": 221965, "content": "不断尝试，反思，把自己以前认知的一些东西推翻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946858}, {"id": 222221, "content": "为什么世界有这么多职位，不能只有一个吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080054}, {"id": 228877, "content": "日子一天天过去，努力画圆！！！圆的终点衔接着新圆的起点！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099982}, {"id": 221966, "content": "付出与收获不成正比", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822334}, {"id": 221967, "content": "越努力越焦虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078749}, {"id": 226319, "content": "看看自己的工资涨幅和杭州的房价增长趋势，我真的完全没有心思工作...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279151}, {"id": 222224, "content": "责任很重", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080060}, {"id": 222225, "content": "情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989466}, {"id": 228113, "content": "人心复杂，个人进步慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099260}, {"id": 222226, "content": "对于未知的焦虑 什么时候是个头呢？", "image": "img/option/option/20170716151912W19483QJRTGwpbNi.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009652}, {"id": 222482, "content": "不知道自己想要什么 不明确珍惜喜欢的是什么 多数人只是在随波逐流或者peer pressure ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081223}, {"id": 221971, "content": "诚信经营，走正道。现在大多忽悠多，违背良知做销售。。", "image": "img/option/option/20170714201721Oag0w4WbYjVZ9Q2L", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024762}, {"id": 221973, "content": "找不到工作的意义，我整天忙碌，想要休息，又是不想休息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051513}, {"id": 221974, "content": "理想与现实的落差感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078756}, {"id": 221975, "content": "学不到东西，吃老本\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 221976, "content": "个人价值决定你的未来！单一的能力已经不足够了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699653}, {"id": 221977, "content": "业绩指标压力，怕检查，怕罚款", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 221978, "content": "30岁的彷徨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078771}, {"id": 221979, "content": "工作一辈子在魔都也不一定能买得起房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075283}, {"id": 221980, "content": "不靠谱的boss，想你自主做事，又不听你的建议……然后乱指挥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487504}, {"id": 221981, "content": "每天虽然有干不完的工作，但是仍然不知道方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076789}, {"id": 222493, "content": "没有工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720660}, {"id": 224029, "content": "感觉什么都不会  但没有学习的意思\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084012}, {"id": 221982, "content": "没有足够的金钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078791}, {"id": 221983, "content": "觉得自己随时可能会被淘汰", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078796}, {"id": 222495, "content": "不成功便成仁", "image": "img/option/option/20170718084008SAg4MTtRefNWvX5l", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010844}, {"id": 231711, "content": "官方脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 234783, "content": "工作一天天忙碌，却失去了动力和兴趣，变得枯燥无味，头晕晕地过着每一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129868}]}